name: Fishy Feeding and Grow 3D
description:
You are a hunter! Feed ! Grow up!

Be an excellent hunter with a huge shark that can grow huge and eat everyone. Rule the underwater world.

Choose from 40 fish and be the biggest. Rule the deep ocean.

Attacked fish will fall apart if you bite into them. Gobble them up.

See how the fish evolve and attack them. Swim faster and faster and collect a lot of energy in the process.

Come and try how much of a surviving monster you can be under the water. In the great deep.

How you can play:

- Choose the fish
- Attack other fish to grow bigger and bigger. Get points for it, which you can use to buy other predators.
